		"description": "مجموعة APIs لتطبيق محام للمعارض\n\nMaham Expo Application API Collection\n\n## Authentication\nAll authenticated endpoints require:\n- `Authorization: Bearer {token}` header\n- Token is obtained from Auth Service (maham-auth-expo-api)\n\n## Languages\nSet `Accept-Language` header to:\n- `ar` - Arabic (default)\n- `en` - English",
